	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_CITY_TRADE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Please Mind The Gap</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_CITY_TRADE_HELP">
			<Text>After years of struggling with planning permission, forced-purchase orders and funding difficulties, the City is finally able to construct a public transportation network.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_CITY_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Release {1_YieldCost} to construct a subway system, gaining {4_GPChange}. The underground generates {3_CityYield} for the City.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_CITY_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>A massive network of underground railways.[NEWLINE]Trains. Underground.[NEWLINE]The future really is here, isn't it?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_CITY_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>A tram system is constructed for {1_YieldCost} and 1 [ICON_RES_IRON] Iron. The City gains {3_CityYield}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_CITY_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>The tram was an incredibly cunning solution to the transport problem. We are going to save so much time and money. Incredible work.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_CITY_TRADE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Impliment a bus service for {1_YieldCost} that improves efficiency at the cost of increased pollution. The City experiences {3_CityYield}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_CITY_TRADE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>When it comes to efficiency, bigger really is better. A shame the same cannot be said for our engine technology.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
	
